# ---- Terraform ----
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup
crash.log
crash.*.log
*.tfvars          # may hold config; commit a *.tfvars.example instead
!*.tfvars.example
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc
# keep the provider lock file committed (do NOT ignore .terraform.lock.hcl)

